    "The rule-based NER known as DrNER comprises two stages in which the first one entails the identification and quantification of the entities mentioned, and the second one entails the choice and extraction of the entities.",
    "The authors also examined the utilizing text corpora from various sources, such as text from a number of scientifically verified websites and text from scientific journals.",
    "The approach was evaluated, and the findings indicated that evidence-based dietary recommendations (drNER) produce good results and may be used to extract knowledge about evidence-based dietary guidelines.",
